Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.04,0:00:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand it anymore, do it faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.08,0:00:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care who it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.08,0:00:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to go without it, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.08,0:00:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever, whatever is fine, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.08,0:00:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to begin the ritual
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.08,0:01:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.08,0:01:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play with me, just give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.08,0:01:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, rape me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.08,0:01:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So you cast your sins
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.08,0:01:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This woman is the Devil in human form
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.08,0:01:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's rid us of her evil
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.08,0:02:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.08,0:02:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you girls want?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.08,0:02:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokitou-san asked that we investigate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.08,0:02:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He still thinks that Tokiwa\NShogo is behind all of this
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.08,0:02:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I have no problem, go ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.48,0:02:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.08,0:03:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, the cause of death was\Nstrangulation, followed by the pole insertion
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the signifigance of "Motsu"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't know. But we're investigating
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Inexcusable! How could someone\Ndo something like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.08,0:03:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, if we don't quickly\Nfind the culprit...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.08,0:03:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There may soon be another victim
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.08,0:03:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you need our help?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.08,0:03:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we'll count on you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Akane!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe-san
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're looking good
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.20,0:03:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm now working at this place
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.08,0:03:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, this is a common everyday inn, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.08,0:04:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,BTW, do you know what "Motsu" means?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,"Motsu?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.08,0:04:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I haven't been helpful
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No worries, thanks. See ya
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.08,0:04:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No, please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little was enough
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.12,0:05:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent bait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask your child what she wants
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So sorry! Move, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.12,0:06:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.12,0:06:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Akane?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.12,0:06:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Akane!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Akane!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be, when she was finally happy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.12,0:06:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't forgive this, I will find you without fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.12,0:07:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry.\NWe've found the culprit
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawaba-san followed the man who left\Nthe body in the river and I caugh him
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.12,0:07:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work Kawaba-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't resist arrest, so it was easy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that imitator from the fair
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.12,0:07:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is Gonzo
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.12,0:07:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He does a great imitation of the Motsu bird,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That would explain why he drew\N"Motsu" on the bodies
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.12,0:07:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,When I saw him, I knew he was the culprit
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He declared his guilt
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.12,0:07:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Of the murders of the two women
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.12,0:07:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I did what God told me to do
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:08:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Zhenwu-san
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.12,0:08:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Zhenwu-san isn't here
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.12,0:08:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't returned for several days
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.12,0:08:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.12,0:08:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.12,0:08:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I haven't seen him in several\Ndays, so I was worried
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.12,0:08:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going where Mikagura-sensei is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.12,0:08:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.12,0:08:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.12,0:08:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's special powder that neutralizes\Nthe effects of opium. Because someone\Nis using it as a weapon
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,For most people the opium\Ncauses hallucinations
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If you start to hallucinate, use it\Nand walk away fast from there
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thanks a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.12,0:09:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew a shower wouldn't be enough,\NI should have gone to Onii-sama
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't just leave her alone
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.12,0:09:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We're animated, so being so depressed\Nis not normal for you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.12,0:09:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so late, I was worried
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.12,0:09:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, there was something\Nthat I had to find out
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Does Gonzo really seem like\Nthe kind of guy to blame?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.16,0:09:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.16,0:09:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I was looking into that Gonzo
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.16,0:09:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He was good at imitating things, not creating\Nthem, so I don't think it was him
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But the bodies had "Motsu" written on them
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be someone else\Nwho wrote "Motsu" on them
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.16,0:09:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, the criminal is someone else
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.16,0:09:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never forgive him! I won't\Nlet these criminals get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,0:09:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:09:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But what'll we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll use some bait
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Bait?! Bait?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The culprit will probably attack again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It should be safe to get him if you wait\Nnear the scenes of the crimes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.16,0:10:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And who will?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.16,0:10:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I will, of course
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.16,0:10:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.16,0:10:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So how can you do that, Kanase-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.16,0:10:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.16,0:10:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The criminal attacks only beautiful girls
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.16,0:10:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And you don't fit that profile
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.16,0:10:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So it should be me who...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.16,0:10:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,With your flat chest and the darkness,\Nhe's bound to think you're a man
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.16,0:10:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.16,0:10:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I speak the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.16,0:10:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls, calm down
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.16,0:10:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, let's have a lottery\Nto see who'll go, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, without records, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.16,0:10:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.16,0:11:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Will she be alright? I should have gone
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.16,0:11:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But I told you that you aren't\Nattractive enough
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.16,0:11:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.16,0:11:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.16,0:11:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Chizuru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let Chizuru-chan go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Shigeno-san
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.16,0:12:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Chizuru-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.16,0:12:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They're over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.20,0:12:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.20,0:12:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokitou-san
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.20,0:12:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't lament what happened\Nwith Sugita-san
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we must concentrate on her rescue
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.20,0:12:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Fanglan-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.20,0:12:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask Zhenwu-san to look for Chizuru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.20,0:12:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that Zhenwu-san... No, my brother\Nhasn't returned home in three days
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.20,0:12:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't returned?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.20,0:12:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine, let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.20,0:12:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But, where?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,To see where Gonzo said he talked to God
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where we'll go
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.18,0:13:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That smell! It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,My body is... heating up
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.20,0:13:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Zhenwu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.20,0:13:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.20,0:14:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Zhenwu-san, resist! Don't\Nyou recognize me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:15:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, you woke up
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.20,0:15:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.20,0:15:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, please calm down
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.20,0:15:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.20,0:15:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.20,0:15:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't control my body
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.20,0:15:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Being like this must be very\Npainful, right Zhenwu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep rubbing it like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.20,0:15:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still hard
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.20,0:15:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this okay? Won't resist?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.20,0:15:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... not that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like? Make me feel good too, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.20,0:16:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Zhenwu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.20,0:16:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... I'm cumming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.20,0:17:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still a bit dazed, but I'm fine
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.20,0:17:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I've done something so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.20,0:17:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I didn't mind doing it with you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,An-Anyway, we've got to get out of here
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.24,0:17:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,My friends are probably on their way,\Nso let's wait here until they arrive
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.24,0:17:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand, until then I'll protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I trust you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.24,0:17:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you here to confess?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.24,0:17:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Then confess your sins, and\Npray for God's forgiveness
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.84,0:18:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the one to confess any\Nsins. How about you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.24,0:18:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who used Gonzo-san\Nto kill your wife Shisue-san\Nand Kuramoto Akane-san
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.24,0:18:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! Why did you do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That woman was guilty, it was all her fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.24,0:18:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.24,0:18:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, give me more, harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.24,0:18:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm cumming!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.24,0:18:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.24,0:18:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly what it looks like!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.24,0:18:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,YOU!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.72,0:18:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What, got a problem? Didn't think so
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:19:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, you're not the one to complain
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what you do, you can't satisfy me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.24,0:19:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that upset you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.24,0:19:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If it bothers you, why not you\Nuse that shit you've got?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.24,0:19:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's your goal, put it here
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.24,0:19:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Although, that's impossible
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to kill my wife, but I couldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.24,0:19:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I listened to the voice of this man
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.24,0:19:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't do it, let someone\Nelse do it for you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If you make Gonzo-san go out of his mind,\Nkilling your wife would be easy
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That woman is a devil, that's\Nwhy you should do it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you go through with\Nit, you'll also be a demon
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.24,0:19:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you do as I say, you'll be fine
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.24,0:20:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I wrote "Motsu" to incriminate Gonzo\Nso he would be arrested
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.24,0:20:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,While writing it, I felt better,\Nbecause I had my revenge
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.24,0:20:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But putting the spike in Shisue-san's\Nbody made me feel good
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,After doing that, I felt liberated
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.24,0:20:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, I couldn't forget that feeling, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.24,0:20:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You used Gonzo-san to kill\NAkane-san, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.24,0:20:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't care who it was, that didn't matter
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.24,0:20:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.24,0:20:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaburagi-san, that's a lie, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.24,0:20:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody told you to assassinate them
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, where is Tokiwa Shogo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.28,0:20:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokitou-san
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.28,0:20:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.28,0:21:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is a passage that leads to\NTokiwa Shogo's secret hideout
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.28,0:21:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Moving forward could be very dangerous
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so I must go, for Akane-san's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.28,0:21:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot let you go alone, Tokitou-san
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.28,0:21:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.28,0:21:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Shigeno-san and Fanglan-chan\Ncan stay with Morimatsu-san
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.28,0:21:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful, Tokitou-sama
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.28,0:21:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think this cave would be so deep
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.28,0:21:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.44,0:22:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.28,0:22:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.28,0:22:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.28,0:22:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokiwa Shogo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.28,0:22:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been awhile
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.28,0:22:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We meet again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.28,0:22:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I welcome you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.28,0:22:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't escape! Surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.28,0:22:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll enjoy this
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.28,0:22:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This shit is opium!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.28,0:22:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you notice? You've tried something\Nyou won't soon forget
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.28,0:23:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No, stop, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.20,0:23:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have some fun
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.28,0:23:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.28,0:23:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Your beloved is being raped in\Nfront of you... Isn't this fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.28,0:23:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to end this
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.28,0:23:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts, somebody...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.28,0:23:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Akane
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.28,0:23:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just like me, Tomoe-san
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.28,0:23:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.28,0:23:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you've also been sold, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.28,0:23:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sold? You're wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.28,0:24:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're doing the same thing as me
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.28,0:24:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been sold, Tomoe-san
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.28,0:24:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sold
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.28,0:24:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If we continue like this, we won't survive
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.28,0:24:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We've no choice but to sell Tomoe
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.28,0:24:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, we'll sell her
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.32,0:24:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't want this!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.32,0:24:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't work, if I'm sold, I won't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.32,0:24:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Save me Tokitou-san! Tokitou-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.32,0:24:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's useless, nobody will come to save you
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.32,0:24:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That was my fate
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.32,0:24:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You can only rely on yourself,\Nand protect yourself alone
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.32,0:24:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it, Tomoe-san
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.32,0:24:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Akane
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.32,0:24:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If you kill him, everything will be alright
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.32,0:24:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.32,0:24:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My mind is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.32,0:24:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Once someone has been hypnotized,\Nit's very easy to do it again
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.32,0:24:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It never fails
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.32,0:25:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, kill this man in\Nfront of you and be free!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.32,0:25:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe-san, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.32,0:25:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up, Tomoe-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.32,0:25:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.32,0:25:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Use this, sensei
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.32,0:25:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to wake up
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.32,0:25:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts! What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.32,0:25:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Heavens, don't you know\Nwhat you were doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.32,0:25:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll deal with that later
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.32,0:25:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so fast, surrender at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.32,0:25:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I was having so much fun, but now\NI'll finish it with my own hands
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.32,0:25:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokitou-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.32,0:25:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Mikagura Tokitou!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.32,0:25:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Good riddance
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.32,0:26:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.32,0:26:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokiwa Shogo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.32,0:26:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop there, Tokiwa Shogo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.32,0:26:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We've blocked all of your escape routes
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.32,0:26:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no escape for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.32,0:26:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I've been defeated
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.32,0:26:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a pretty fun game, Mikagura Tokitou
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.32,0:26:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finished, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.32,0:27:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I will ensure that he pays\Nfor his crimes, I swear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.32,0:27:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's head back to Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.32,0:27:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We're finally going back to Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.32,0:27:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Fanglan, you're coming to Japan too?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.32,0:27:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Shigeno-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.35,0:27:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.35,0:27:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, Ranmaru
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.35,0:27:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She hadn't noticed
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.35,0:27:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sure, of course I had noticed!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.35,0:27:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, shall we go Tokitou-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.35,0:27:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.35,0:27:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot, for all of your help
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.35,0:27:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care, Shakuryu-san
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.35,0:27:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for all of your help, Zhenwu-san
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.35,0:27:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.35,0:27:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget you Chizuru-san,\Nor Mikagura-sensei
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.35,0:28:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They get along well!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.35,0:28:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.35,0:28:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't make fun of me
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.35,0:28:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, Shigeno-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.35,0:28:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, now's the time to go
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.35,0:28:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Yes. Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.36,0:29:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.36,0:29:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Little early to be scandalous, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.36,0:29:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wounds are already healed?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.36,0:29:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I feel perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.36,0:29:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe-kun, we have a new case.\NWill you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.36,0:29:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, Tokitou-san!